lead_paragraph: Makayla Epps scored 29 points, Evelyn Akhator had 18 points and 10 rebounds, and No. 19 Kentucky opened its season with an 82-66 win over No. 14 Miami in the Kentucky Classic on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Epps Helps No. 19 Kentucky Women Top No. 14 Miami 82-66
